      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-5">
        <div class="flex gap-5 p-6 rounded-lg bg-surface-base border border-surface-border">
          <span class="font-black text-ab-green text-[1.5rem] leading-none shrink-0 w-8">01</span>
          <p class="text-[#ccc] text-[0.95rem] leading-[1.65]"><strong class="text-white">Do not recreate the AB monogram using any typeface.</strong> The lettermark is custom-drawn. Any version made from a font — including condensed sans-serifs — is not acceptable.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-5 p-6 rounded-lg bg-surface-base border border-surface-border">
          <span class="font-black text-ab-green text-[1.5rem] leading-none shrink-0 w-8">02</span>
          <p class="text-[#ccc] text-[0.95rem] leading-[1.65]"><strong class="text-white">Do not convert Neon Green to CMYK for process print.</strong> #00FF1F is fluorescent and falls outside the CMYK gamut. Use for digital or Pantone spot printing only.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-5 p-6 rounded-lg bg-surface-base border border-surface-border">
          <span class="font-black text-ab-green text-[1.5rem] leading-none shrink-0 w-8">03</span>
          <p class="text-[#ccc] text-[0.95rem] leading-[1.65]"><strong class="text-white">Do not use the AB monogram and logo simultaneously in a sponsor lockup.</strong> They serve different institutional roles. Together with a partner mark the result is overcrowded and confusing.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-5 p-6 rounded-lg bg-surface-base border border-surface-border">
          <span class="font-black text-ab-green text-[1.5rem] leading-none shrink-0 w-8">04</span>
          <p class="text-[#ccc] text-[0.95rem] leading-[1.65]"><strong class="text-white">Do not place any mark on a low-contrast background.</strong> The AB Green monogram requires sufficient contrast. Avoid mid-tone greens or olives. Use white or gold versions instead.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-5 p-6 rounded-lg bg-surface-base border border-surface-border">
          <span class="font-black text-ab-green text-[1.5rem] leading-none shrink-0 w-8">05</span>
          <p class="text-[#ccc] text-[0.95rem] leading-[1.65]"><strong class="text-white">Do not stretch, distort, or unevenly scale any mark.</strong> All logos, monograms, and lockups must be scaled proportionally at all times, without exception.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-5 p-6 rounded-lg bg-surface-base border border-surface-border">
          <span class="font-black text-ab-green text-[1.5rem] leading-none shrink-0 w-8">06</span>
          <p class="text-[#ccc] text-[0.95rem] leading-[1.65]"><strong class="text-white">Do not use off-brand typefaces as substitutes for ABC Camera Plain.</strong> When unavailable, Helvetica is the only approved temporary fallback. No display fonts, scripts, or other sans-serifs.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-5 p-6 rounded-lg bg-surface-base border border-surface-border md:col-span-2">
          <span class="font-black text-ab-green text-[1.5rem] leading-none shrink-0 w-8">07</span>
          <p class="text-[#ccc] text-[0.95rem] leading-[1.65]"><strong class="text-white">Do not editorialize the club's heritage claims.</strong> Championship years and honours are official record. Do not abbreviate, omit, or approximate history.</p>
